{"tid":2161530,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴選巴塞2000年起最佳收購","createTime":"2020-08-17T15:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T09:17:17.000Z","uid":28938,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"6fd716224833fcdc28035e04d4f859d4492bc5e3","tid":2161530,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:00:44.000Z","msg":"1. 朗拿甸奴<br />\n符合球會風格嘅森巴球王，幫球會攞到幾多榮譽唔使講，再加帶起埋美斯，間接建立咗20年嘅巴塞皇朝。<br />\n<br />\n2. 伊度奧<br />\n巴塞歷代最強射手之一，最重要同美斯夾到，加埋佢之前係皇馬走漏眼嘅球員，巴塞獨具慧眼更加激死死敵。<br />\n<br />\n3. 戴維斯<br />\n巴塞2004年陷入墮落期時加盟成為及時雨，幫巴塞整季追番唔少分數，佢鬥牛梗嘅性格亦激勵返成隊球隊，最重要嘅係佢冇得罪嗰時初出道時嘅美斯。"},{"pid":"3cfc9190161123b77781fe450a3081f695113bb2","tid":2161530,"uid":80624,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"丹尼爾艾維斯"},{"pid":"2d7ef2d7132f0f50fcd5595baad8371541efd121","tid":2161530,"uid":40757,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"美斯<br />\n2000年<br />\n紐維爾舊生轉會巴塞隆拿"},{"pid":"629db8321e90068e5d432080bf60114c3a7d5b8a","tid":2161530,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"碧基"},{"pid":"1f22fb66dd265a4cb9cb58150fc3c421db67b4c2","tid":2161530,"uid":72476,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"蘇亞雷斯/尼馬都冇<br />\n有戴維斯！？"},{"pid":"578a7949bab8bd4f2057a9f478bfdc12d7eb39b8","tid":2161530,"uid":226156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:07:22.000Z","msg":"基本上夢三成隊都係，甚至乎後備嘅拿臣"},{"pid":"b04b69c4ccc90f64b8b152759f11ae7222a3c9f0","tid":2161530,"uid":179547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:07:45.000Z","msg":"古天奴"},{"pid":"77225a1eafb45038af114004352dcca7048e364c","tid":2161530,"uid":160622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f22fb66dd265a4cb9cb58150fc3c421db67b4c2","tid":2161530,"uid":72476,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:06:28.000Z","msg":"蘇亞雷斯/